				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{{FS}}}_i = \frac{{{\mathrm{{exp}}}\left( { - \frac{{\Delta G_i}}{{k_{\mathrm{{B}}}T}}} \right)}}{{1 + {\mathrm{{exp}}}\left( { - \frac{{\Delta G_i}}{{k_{\mathrm{{B}}}T}}} \right)}},\Delta G_i = G_{ - 1,i} - G_{0,i}\, \Longrightarrow \, \Delta G_i = - k_{\mathrm{{B}}}T\,{\mathrm{ln}}\left( {\frac{{{\mathrm{{FS}}}_i}}{{1 - {\mathrm{{FS}}}_i}}} \right).$$\end{document}FSi=exp−ΔGikBT1+exp−ΔGikBT,ΔGi=G−1,i−G0,i⇒ΔGi=−kBTlnFSi1−FSi.

